HEADWORD: nightie
<hw>nightie</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Any loose-fitting
clothing for wear in bed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Especially:</specif> <def>a loose dress designed
to be worn in bed by women; a nightgown.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nightgown, night-robe, nightdress.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nightingale</ent>⟦br⟧
